{"title":"西部之春","authors":["高占祥"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":4,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西部之春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高占祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一缕春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹绿连绵的山峰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道春潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溶化久冻的冰层。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤醒苍茫的大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞出缤纷的彩虹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，西部大开发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中国走进春天的脚步；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，西部大开发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是神州播种理想的行动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西部———"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这片神奇的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孕育了多少人类的文明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从莫高窟的飞天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到麦积山的石经；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从楼兰遗址的陶片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到丝绸古道的驼铃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的每一个地名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都令我们向往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的每一个传说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都让世界震惊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而每当我翻开历史画卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复杂的情感就从心底萌生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从“春风不度玉门关”的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咏叹中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感到西部苍岩的寒冷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从“大漠风尘日色昏”的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描绘里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我品味出这里的荒凉与"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫穷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那悲凉的诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲壮的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲怆的羌笛声啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次萦绕在梦中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，在这里———"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花与杂草并存，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琴声与风声交融。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文明与愚昧同在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富有与贫穷共生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今———"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴随着潇潇的春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐浴着浩荡的春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广袤博大的西部啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如一只展翅欲飞的大鹏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊———"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的西部人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正开拓着五彩的人生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大漠孤烟何所惧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦斗如饴骨铮铮："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向贫困宣战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向荒凉抗争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向戈壁要奇珍异宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向旷野要五谷丰登。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向村镇要熙熙攘攘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向荒山要郁郁葱葱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向沼泽要康庄大道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向沙漠要柳绿花红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向瀚海要油龙翻滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向草原要万马奔腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向改革要摩天大厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向开放要两个文明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向市场要繁华似锦啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向科学要百业兴隆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，西部响起的誓言掷地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———我们不靠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———我们不等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———我们不退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———我们不停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷而思变不失志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富而思源不忘穷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首迈向新世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着困难去出征！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信东风唤不回啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信春来花不红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，西部大开发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是大地向阳光的宣誓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，西部大开发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是森林与群山的共鸣："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———东西南北中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是亲弟兄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———东西南北中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个大家庭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———东西南北中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拧成一股绳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———东西南北中啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合力大无穷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同洒汗水同鼓劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共创大业共繁荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让富饶文明的西部之春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们的手中诞生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让伟大祖国的上空啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再腾起一条冲天的巨龙！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}